al y billing a develop.<br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><time datetime=\"2023-10-03\" /> </p></td><td><p> <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"622640bedb58c100687be853\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Yesterday: <br />Today: Levantando billing y no se pudo avanzar mucho. Avanzando con v portal.<br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>2</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:ef9f10ea-d622-4072-8c75-6176eaefcb76\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Today: Hoy est&aacute; terminando lo de vportal. Asi avanza Bruno.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><time datetime=\"2023-10-02\" /> </p></td><td><p> <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"622640bedb58c100687be853\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Yesterday: Jueves fue el contexto de la iniciativa.<br />Today: Tratando de levantar el ambiente local.<br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>1</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2705915915"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":372},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2705915915/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2705915915/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2705915915/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2705915915/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2705915915","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2705915915/CFT+JPOS+Sync","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN